Thik hai! Push karne ke liye mujhe kuch details chahiye:

1. **GitHub Repository URL** - Aapka repo link kya hai? (https://github.com/username/repo-name)
2. **Branch name** - Kaunsa branch use karna hai? (usually `main` ya `master`)

